","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"code":"shape","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"title":"MLNShapeSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"  protocol is used to provide details about geographic features"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contained in an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. Each concrete"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in turn has a subclass that conforms to this protocol. A"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature object associates a shape with an optional identifier and attributes."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature","title":"MLNFeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature/attributes":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"attributes"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature\/attributes","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A dictionary of attributes for this feature."}],"title":"attributes","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature\/attributes","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"